# SHError.Code.customCatalogInvalid

**Case**

The error code to indicate when the custom catalog fails to load due to an invalid format.

## Declaration

```swift
case customCatalogInvalid
```

## Catalog errors

- **SHError.Code.customCatalogInvalidURL**: The error code to indicate that the format for the custom catalog URL is invalid.
